headline.main: Navy Ball to Help Britain; Event Nov. 26 Is in Honor of Officers and Enlisted Men

lead_paragraph: The latest in the series of events arranged this season in behalf of Bundles for Britain is a Navy Ball, which will be given by that war relief organization, in cooperation with the Navy League of the United States, on the night of Nov. 26 in the grand ballroom of the Waldorf-Astoria.
abstract: Bundles for Brit benefit Navy Ball planned, N Y C
